### File Manager — REST API 测试文件
### 使用 VS Code REST Client 插件 (humao.rest-client) 运行
### 前置条件: 后端已启动 (cd backend && mvn quarkus:dev)

# ---- 基础配置 ----
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@apiFiles = {{baseUrl}}/api/files
@apiTags = {{baseUrl}}/api/tags
@apiBatch = {{baseUrl}}/api/batch
@apiDupes = {{baseUrl}}/api/duplicates

# ============================================================
# 文件浏览与搜索
# ============================================================

### 1. 健康检查
GET {{apiFiles}}/ping

### 2. 浏览用户主目录
GET {{apiFiles}}?path=C:\Users\34389

### 3. 浏览桌面
GET {{apiFiles}}?path=C:\Users\34389\Desktop

### 4. 按文件名搜索
GET {{apiFiles}}/search?q=pom.xml&type=NAME&page=0&size=20

### 5. 按文件内容搜索
GET {{apiFiles}}/search?q=FileManager&type=CONTENT&page=0&size=20

### 6. 搜索 + 扩展名过滤
GET {{apiFiles}}/search?q=.java&type=NAME&page=0&size=10

# ============================================================
# 文件操作
# ============================================================

### 7. 复制文件
POST {{apiFiles}}/copy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "E:/local/test/test.txt",
  "destination": "E:/local/test/test_copy.txt"
}

### 8. 移动文件
POST {{apiFiles}}/move
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "E:/local/test/test_copy.txt",
  "destination": "E:/local/test/test_moved.txt"
}

### 9. 重命名文件
PUT {{apiFiles}}/rename
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "E:/local/test/test_moved.txt",
  "newName": "renamed.txt"
}

### 10. 删除文件
DELETE {{apiFiles}}?path=E:/local/test/renamed.txt

# ============================================================
# 文件索引 (搜索前必须先索引)
# ============================================================

### 10a. 同步索引 (立即处理，适合小目录)
POST {{apiFiles}}/index?path=E:/local/file-manager/backend/src

### 10b. Kafka 异步索引 (提交到消息队列后台处理，适合大目录)
POST {{apiFiles}}/index/async?path=E:/local/file-manager/backend/src

# ============================================================
# 标签管理
# ============================================================

### 11. 创建标签
POST {{apiTags}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Java Source",
  "color": "#F59E0B",
  "description": "Java 源代码文件"
}

### 12. 创建子标签
POST {{apiTags}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Quarkus Config",
  "color": "#10B981",
  "description": "Quarkus 配置文件",
  "parentId": 1
}

### 13. 列出所有标签
GET {{apiTags}}

### 14. 更新标签
PUT {{apiTags}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Java Source Code",
  "color": "#EF4444"
}

### 15. 删除标签
DELETE {{apiTags}}/1

# ============================================================
# 批量操作
# ============================================================

### 16. 提交批量任务
POST {{apiBatch}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "COPY",
  "tasks": [
    {"operation": "COPY", "source": "E:\\local\\test\\a.txt", "destination": "E:\\local\\test\\backup\\a.txt"},
    {"operation": "COPY", "source": "E:\\local\\test\\b.txt", "destination": "E:\\local\\test\\backup\\b.txt"},
    {"operation": "DELETE", "source": "E:\\local\\test\\old.txt", "destination": ""}
  ]
}

### 17. 查询批量任务进度
GET {{apiBatch}}/1

# ============================================================
# 批量操作
# ============================================================

### 18. 扫描重复文件
POST {{apiDupes}}/scan?rootPath=E:\local\test

### 19. 列出所有重复组
GET {{apiDupes}}

### 20. 清理重复文件 (保留最旧)
DELETE {{apiDupes}}/1?keepPolicy=oldest

# ============================================================
# WebSocket (使用 wscat 或浏览器控制台测试)
# ============================================================

### WebSocket 连接测试:
# wscat -c ws://localhost:8080/ws/file-monitor
# > {"action":"watch","path":"E:/local/test"}
#
# wscat -c ws://localhost:8080/ws/batch-progress/1
# (自动每 2 秒推送进度)

# ============================================================
# OpenAPI 文档
# ============================================================

### Swagger UI
# 浏览器访问: http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui

### OpenAPI JSON
# http://localhost:8080/openapi

# ============================================================
# 拓展功能 #5 #6 #8 #9
# ============================================================

### 21. 文件统计仪表盘
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats/dashboard

### 22. 正则搜索
GET {{apiFiles}}/search?q=Resource&regex=true&type=NAME

### 23. 正则 + 高级过滤
GET {{apiFiles}}/search?q=Service&regex=true&type=NAME&sizeMin=1000&sizeMax=10000&extension=java

### 24. 导出 JSON
GET {{apiFiles}}/search/export?q=Resource&regex=true&type=NAME&format=json

### 25. 导出 CSV
GET {{apiFiles}}/search/export?q=Resource&regex=true&type=NAME&format=csv

### 26. 创建文件规则
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "清理临时文件",
  "pattern": "*.tmp",
  "actionType": "DELETE",
  "rootPath": "E:/local/test",
  "enabled": false
}

### 27. 列出所有规则
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rules

### 28. 执行规则
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rules/1/execute

### 29. 更新规则
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/rules/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enabled": true
}

### 30. 删除规则
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/rules/1
